############################################################
# Data & outputs (case-sensitive project DATA directory)
# Strategy:
#  - Keep small raw reference CSV/XLSX tracked (DATA/ root)
#  - Ignore heavy generated artifacts: processed, cache, temp, exports
#  - Ignore GIS heavy files while allowing a canonical boundary set
#  - Allow notebooks/outputs for versioned analytical notebooks
############################################################

# Legacy lowercase patterns (retain for safety if used elsewhere)
/data/**/processed/
/data/**/outputs/

# Project level generic outputs directory
outputs/

## Simplified DATA subfolders (keep only raw, processed, cache)
DATA/processed/
DATA/cache/

# Ignore contents of processed & cache (raw stays tracked)
DATA/processed/**
DATA/cache/**

# Allow placeholder keep files & README for documentation
!DATA/**/.gitkeep
!DATA/README.md

# GIS heavy files ignored globally except explicit whitelist (optional remove if you want to track)
DATA/**/*.shp
DATA/**/*.shx
DATA/**/*.dbf
DATA/**/*.cpg
DATA/**/*.prj
DATA/**/*.geojson
DATA/**/*.gpkg

# Whitelist canonical boundary set (kept for now)
!DATA/BND_ADM_DONG_PG/**

# (Removed) notebooks/outputs rules cleaned up after consolidation into root outputs/

